               <placeName>ʾAgärhǝse ʾAbunä Mamas</placeName>
               <placeName type="alt">Däbrä Qǝddusan ʾAbunä Mamas ʾAgärhǝse</placeName>
               <country>Ethiopia</country>
               <region>Tǝgray</region>
               <settlement from="2010-11-16" to="2010-11-16">wäräda Gulo Mäkäda, ṭabiya Šäwit Lämläm, qušät ʾAgärhǝse</settlement>
               <location>
                  <geo>14.44875 39.342167</geo>
                  <height unit="m">2312.0</height>
               </location>
               <note>
                  <date type="foundation" notBefore="1300" notAfter="1400">1300-1400</date>
                  <desc type="foundation">The date provided by the local tradition is 1295 year of mercy.</desc>
                  <ab type="history">Gätär. According to the Vita of saint Bä-ṣälotä Mikaʾel of Däbrä Gol (ʾAmhara), he was exiled to Gulo Mäkäda and died at Gwǝdgwǝde, which seems to have been a name of the area around ʾAgärhǝse. Local tradition remembers him and confirms that his burial place is in the vicinity. &#xD;
Tabots (4): Mary, Michael, Mamas, Raphael.</ab>
                  <ab type="description">25 Mss.; 10 Mss. photographed: <ref target="ESaqm001">AQM-001</ref> "Vita of Mamas"; <ref target="ESaqm002">AQM-002</ref> "Vita of Mamas"; <ref target="ESaqm003">AQM-003</ref> "Four Gospels"; <ref target="ESaqm004">AQM-004</ref> "The Book of the Baptismal Rite"; <ref target="ESaqm005">AQM-005</ref> "Miracles of Jesus"; <ref target="ESaqm006">AQM-006</ref> "Miracles of Mary"; <ref target="ESaqm007">AQM-007</ref> "Miracles of Jesus"; <ref target="ESaqm008">AQM-008</ref> "Missal"; <ref target="ESaqm009">AQM-009</ref> "Missal"; <ref target="ESaqm010">AQM-010</ref> "The Book of the Funeral Rite"</ab>
